My favorite lunch spot with my colleagues. They have very nice air (cukup manis) and plenty of food options to order. It's not very crowded and a good place if you wish to eat alone.
Open till late night, good roti
Came here for dinner or supper every now then. The food here is nice, the staff are friendly and the environment is cosy and clean.
It was such an amazing time at your place. The food was superb. Thank you for giving me a flavourful meal to enjoyy👍
